Package api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BuildingApi
    Main API interface for Buildings with RetroFit2 Allows for the posting of a single building and allows for the retrieval of a building by its landlord
    LambdaInterface<T>  
    LandlordApi
    Main API interface for Landlord with RetroFit2 Allows for the posting of a single Landlord by path or body and allows for the retrieval of all landlord or a single one by its email and password
    MaintenanceApi
    Main API interface for Maintenance Requests with RetroFit2 Allows for the posting of Maintenance Requests by path, and request a maintenance request object by all or by email of tenant who posted it.
    PostApi  
    RentApi
    Main API interface for Rent with RetroFit2.
    TenantApi
    Main API interface for Tenants with RetroFit2 Allows for the posting of a single tenant by body or path, and allows the app to get all tenants or a tenant by its email and password
    UnitApi
    Main API for Units with RetroFit2 Allows for posting a building object by a path and getting a building by its unique id
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApiClientFactory
    Main API client factory class that sends requests to http client with RetroFit2
